comments: Hardaway Jr. (DAL) makes marginal contact with Jackson's (LAC) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Kennard (LAC) places his hands momentarily to Porzingis' (DAL) side prior to his upward shooting motion.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) makes incidental contact with Kennard (LAC) arm after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Mann (LAC) firms up and absorbs the contact.
George (LAC) places a hand/arm to the front of Hardaway Jr. (DAL) on the drive and the contact affects his SQBR.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) places a hand/arm to the front of Jackson (LAC) during the drive but the contact is marginal and does not affect Jackson's SQBR.
George (LAC) is last to make contact with the ball, as it goes OOB and he makes an attempt to save it.
Morris Sr. (LAC) grabs the jersey of Porzingis (DAL) off ball as he is setting a screen during the inbound play.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) commits a take foul on George (LAC).
Mann (LAC) does not inbound the ball within the five seconds allotted to his team.
George (LAC) commits a take foul on Kleber (DAL).
George (LAC) does not gain possession of the ball until his left foot is planted and he takes two legal steps landing on his right to establish his pivot foot prior to the upward shooting motion.
